metadata.title: Copper River Delta Wetlands Vegetation

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest, Cordova Ranger District contract with Ducks Unlimited Inc.

metadata.description: Data Type: Vegetation/Land Cover/Soils;  Copper River Delta remotely sensed wetlands vegetation map. The data is intended to assist in assessing the size, shape, and distribution of the vegetation community types since the 1994 earthquake uplifted the delta. It will be incorporated into the forest wide landcover dataset and assist in assessing vegetation succession and wildlife habitat.
